Subject: [PATCH] cryptodev: allow copying EVP contexts

Forward port of patch from:
https://rt.openssl.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=2770&user=guest&pass=guest

Signed-off-by: Javier Viguera <javier.viguera@digi.com>
